    "steps": [
        "Rinse the basmati rice thoroughly and soak for 30 minutes. Drain.",
        "In a mixing bowl, marinate chicken pieces with yogurt, salt, turmeric, cumin, coriander, and garam masala. Let it sit for 15 minutes.",
        "In a large pot, heat oil or ghee and sauté sliced onions until golden brown.",
        "Add garlic and ginger, sauté for 2 minutes until fragrant.",
        "Add the marinated chicken and cook until it is browned and partially cooked through.",
        "Add soaked and drained rice to the pot and mix well with the chicken and onions.",
        "Add cinnamon stick and saffron, stir to combine.",
        "Pour in the water and bring to a boil. Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20-25 minutes until the rice is fully cooked and the chicken is tender.",
